Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:38.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}藏于左手的愿望终归只是愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:43.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}空梦一场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:46.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}宿于右手的空虚记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:50.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}于无人知晓的世界尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:55.61,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}被无尽的雨水打湿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:03:01.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}守护想要守护之物的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:06.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}无法相信这一切的脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:11.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}接受一切 探求明日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:14.27,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}勇敢之光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:19.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}伸出手去你会见到光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:25.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}遍体伤痕的你会看到我的光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:29.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}于高举的剑尖处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:31.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}将思绪交织
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:38.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}心愿超越时空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:44.94,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你的勇敢之光
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== OPJP ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:38.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}左手に隠した願いは願いのままで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:43.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}冴えない夢を見た
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:46.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}右手には空の記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:50.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}誰も知らない世界の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:55.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}止まない雨に打たれていた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:03:01.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}守りたいものを守れる強さ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:06.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}それを信じられなくなるひ弱さ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:11.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}すべてを受け入れて　明日を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:14.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Brave Shine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:19.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}手を伸ばせばnow you see the light
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:25.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}傷だらけにnow you see my light
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:29.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}翳した刃の先に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:31.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}思いを重ねた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:38.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}祈りは時を超えて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:44.94,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Your brave shine
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== EDCN ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:09.84,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}如果心终会消失不再
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.09,0:22:13.88,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}至少纵声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:25.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}恸哭和绝望之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:31.11,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}等待我们的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.73,0:22:38.45,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}都不过是生命梦想的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.74,0:22:41.37,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}为之奋斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.62,0:22:46.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}当下的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:53.01,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你哭泣的夜晚之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.09,0:22:59.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}藏有遥远未来的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:03.77,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}静谧在等待你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.06,0:23:09.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}耀眼的丘陵 必能到达
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.19,0:23:15.61,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你所在的地平线
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.90,0:23:21.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}奏响你的心铃
